
Background: 

Harizanov and Gribanova 2015 claim that conjoined singular marked adjectives can modify plural nouns in Bulgarian.
Three constrains have been observed: 1. no mismatch in number values, 2. no suppletive plural forms on the noun, 3. no plurale tantum.
However, all the examples in H&G involve only one definite article. Patterns with two DPs with definite articles seem to be different.

1.	părvata			i		posledna stranic-i
		first.sg.def and last.sg 	pages.pl

A.sg.def and A.sg.def N.sg is much better than N.pl. Compare \Next and \NNext:

2.	Skanirai mi parvata i poslednata stranitsi
		scan me first.sg.def and last.sg.def page.pl

3.	parvata i poslednata stranitsa.sg (better than \Last)
		first.sg.def and last.sf.def page.sg.

A.sg and A.sg N.pl is not good if N is human as in \Next. Same thing goes to Children, Mothers, Brothers, Guitar players, Artists


4. 
-	Which (music) band did u like from the show?

-	purvata i poslednata banda/*bandi
	first.sg.def and last.sg.def band.sg/*band.pl

As is claimed by Harizanov and Gribanova 2015, A.sg and A.sg N.pl is not good if N.pl is a suppletive form as in \Nextt

5. a. Person = chovek, People = dushi
	 b. *purviat i posleniat dushi 
	 		 first.sg.def and last.sg.def people.pl
	 c. purviat i posleniat chovek
      first.sg.def and last.sg.def person.sg

Unlike what's claimbed by Harizanov and Gribanova 2015, mismatches in number is allowed if the noun shows agreement with the closest conjunct (CCA), as is shown in \Next.

6. 	Parvata i poslednite stranitsi
		first.sg.def and last.pl.def pages.pl
 
7.	Skanirai mi purvata i poslednite 5 stranitsi
		scan me first.sg.def and last.pl.def 5 page.pl
		‘6 pages in total’
		
8.	Skanirai mi purvite i poslednite 5 stranitsi
		scan me first.pl.def and last.pl.def page.pl
		`10 pages in total’

9.	*părv-i i posledn-a stranic-i
		first.pl and last.sg page.pl

10.	*Skanirai mi purvite 20 i poslednata stranitsi
		scan me first.pl.def 20 and last.sg.def page.pl
	
11.	Skanirai mi purvite 20 i poslednata stranitsa
		scan me first.pl.def 20 and last.sg.def page.sg

12.	Skanirai mi parvata i poslednite 25 stranitsi
		scan me first.sg.def and last.pl.def 25 page.pl

I am sure that with humans it's unacceptable

13. We are watching Dancing with the stars and you fall asleep on and off
Later you ask me which contestants you missed and I say:\\

propusna purvia i poslednia 	sustezatel / *sustezateli
					            Masc masc {masc.sg / *pl}

14.	
- Which (music) band did u like from the show?
- I liked purvata i poslednata banda/*bandi

Gender mismatch is not allowed when the shared noun is plural.

15.	*first.masc and last.fem piano players (gender mismatch + pl noun)

Question: first.masc and last.fem piano player (gender mismatch + sg noun)







